<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q48_v9" title="Q48_v9" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>La suma de cuatro de cinco números es <m:math><m:mn>260</m:mn></m:math>, y el promedio de los cinco números es <m:math><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math>. El quinto número es x.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuál es el valor de x?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">20<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si el promedio de 5 números es <m:math><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la suma total de los 5 números es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>70</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>350</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como cuatro de ellos suman <m:math><m:mn>260</m:mn></m:math>, el quinto debe ser <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>350</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>260</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math> no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">90<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si el promedio de 5 números es <m:math><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math>, la suma total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>70</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>350</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como la suma de cuatro números es <m:math><m:mn>260</m:mn></m:math>, el quinto número es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>350</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>260</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces, <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">70<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El promedio es <m:math><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math>, pero eso no significa que el quinto número sea <m:math><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math>. La suma total de los 5 números es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>70</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>350</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Luego, el quinto número debe ser <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>350</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>260</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math> no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">65<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La suma total de los 5 números, usando el promedio, es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>70</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>350</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Si cuatro números suman <m:math><m:mn>260</m:mn></m:math>, entonces el quinto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>350</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>260</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>65</m:mn></m:math> no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Usar el promedio para hallar la suma total de los cinco números</strong></p>
            <p>Si el promedio de 5 números es <m:math><m:mn>70</m:mn></m:math>, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>70</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>350</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>La suma de los cinco números es <m:math><m:mn>350</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Restar la suma de los cuatro números conocidos</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado dice que la suma de cuatro de los cinco números es <m:math><m:mn>260</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces el quinto número es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>350</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>260</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular la diferencia</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>350</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>260</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El valor de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> es <m:math><m:mn>90</m:mn></m:math>, por lo tanto la alternativa correcta es la B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>